'''Minisiteri y'Ibikorwa Remezo''' ( '''MININFRA''' ; Kinyarwanda    ; French    ) ni ishami rya  
[[Dosiye:Ikiraro.jpg|thumb|Ikiraro]]
Guverinoma y'u [[Rwanda]] . Minisiteri ishinzwe politiki y'ibikorwa remezo n'iterambere mu gihugu hose. Claver Gatete ni Minisitiri w’ibikorwa Remezo muri guverinoma ya Rwanda. Mbere yibyo, yakoreye Guverinoma ye mu nzego zitandukanye; Minisitiri w’imari n’igenamigambi mu bukungu (2013-2018); Guverineri wa Banki Nkuru y’u [[Rwanda]] (2011-2013) na Komiseri Mukuru mu Bwongereza, Irilande na Isilande, (2005 - 2009). 

